{"tid":2512661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遊樂場「另類滑梯」布滿浮雕顛簸不平  　網民諷「玩一次都好傷」","createTime":"2021-05-02T02:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T02:53:28.000Z","uid":271829,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c6683ba953bf454a5e327560fc563c8f6852db73","tid":2512661,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:14:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/none/a9abbf7b911c8084ac04863c290e0838/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210501/_2021050120110836611.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2Fa9abbf7b911c8084ac04863c290e0838%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210501%2F_2021050120110836611.jpg&h=f09b1333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民諷刺一處遊樂場的滑梯布滿浮雕，如同「刑具」。<br />\n<br />\n兒童遊樂場中時常見的滑梯，一般都是平滑的，但是近日網上圖片流傳了一條「另類滑梯」，引發了網民熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n有網民日前在「今日有嘢講」社交群組發圖，圖中所見，在一處兒童遊樂場一個似是滑梯的遊樂設施上，布滿了動物與昆蟲浮雕圖案，顛簸不平。可想而知，玩這條「滑梯」的孩子，大概都不能從上面往下溜。帖文更帶諷刺的問道：「這是什麼刑具？ 」<br />\n<br />\n至於網民們看到這道「另類滑梯」，部分都跟隨嘲諷，認為是中看不中用，更隨時令玩者受傷「一條滑不到的滑梯」「 玩一次已懷疑人生」 「玩一次，都好傷 」。<br />\n<br />\n當中亦有人相信，這條「另類滑梯」實際是一種讓兒童攀爬的遊樂設施，並不是單純滑梯：「應該係爬上爬落既 」「爬上去架， 比d創意啦」「其實見到後面有條綠色滑梯囉。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/621210298364869/posts/1094762864342941/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F621210298364869%2Fposts%2F1094762864342941%2F&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=02b1181d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/621210298364869/posts/1094762864342941/</a>"},{"pid":"069adcf6a1f950de0844ada1ba1a92747bc23c0b","tid":2512661,"uid":244113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:19:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eee0ac88749c1ccea8fa8679f5be1f75aeec91c","tid":2512661,"uid":308251,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:21:30.000Z","msg":"屌你老母政府班人個腦裝屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334c326675eed5437fbe4ec52271e523237b54e2","tid":2512661,"uid":155818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:22:33.000Z","msg":"邊個弱能治咁反社會設計埋D閪野<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7168403f4494665fead50ed0ee91bcd871b16a56","tid":2512661,"uid":70769,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:23:27.000Z","msg":"我都覺得係攀爬用，但係斜道唔夠高唔會好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc15fa48d2fb1d4e45361f9a7e96516ca0c9b8c","tid":2512661,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:23:48.000Z","msg":"係咪玩填色比賽？"},{"pid":"28e5efdf2b0b5c43e14173b0267f9f3b8bc01407","tid":2512661,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:26:20.000Z","msg":"政府班人真係垃圾<br />\n整智障噴泉、滑梯<br />\n以為九龍皇帝啲字係文宣清左<br />\n防疫柒柒下整四級複雜到冇咩人想去了解<br />\n<br />\n由最上至最下都係柒到飛"},{"pid":"18023781aca2f496321ae641d3d88d5072a6d57b","tid":2512661,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:29:37.000Z","msg":"御路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/御路\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%BE%A1%E8%B7%AF&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=b2d0c0e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/御路</a>"},{"pid":"845cb476773524d41419ec0dfdbc6db69f8a4a14","tid":2512661,"uid":147380,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:31:28.000Z","msg":"爬上去㗎  換哂呢啲就啱㗎啦  好多賤種掉轉玩滑梯踩污糟哂"},{"pid":"2808939c2ff8d3a0c815b8311d19a45d97255970","tid":2512661,"uid":57844,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:32:35.000Z","msg":"好明顯係爬啦<br />\n小朋友見到咁自然識玩爬<br />\n網民智商仲低過小朋友"},{"pid":"18f3a60de05406b92c5e99e8f821865cbf7795c2","tid"